summary: Who’s Taylor swift anyways please describe her to me
question: Who’s Taylor swift anyways please describe her to me
answer: Taylor Swift is one of the most kind hearted, warming and loving people, luckily, I have met. She loves baking, sewing and painting and does this on days off but also does these things to give as gifts. She has a strong personality with a soft heart. She has the best group of friends and family that unconditionally support and love her. She is a gloabal superstar that has dominated in country music and now pop music. She’s one of the most awarded woman of our generation winning a Grammy for album of the year not once but twice. She has broken sooo many records I can’t count. She loves her fans more than I’ve ever known, has inside jokes with us, wants to meet us, puts on tours for us and most importantly she listens to us. She could be called mitochondria because she really is a powerhouse. But mostly she’s a 29 year old wonderful woman from Pennsylvania that has changed so many lives with her music including mine.

summary: I would love to see Taylor publicly speaking about the environment/promoting positive environmental changes. Even just speaking...
body: I would love to see Taylor publicly speaking about the environment/promoting positive environmental changes. Even just speaking out about what’s happening to the planet. I know I sound boring but it’s something I’m really passionate about and I feel like if Taylor spoke more about protecting and helping the planet people would listen. They listened when she promoted voting (💓🙌🏼) so what’s stopping people from listening about this? @taylorswift I know it’s no where in the job description but I would be so eternally grateful 💗
